    <p class="about-p r d2" data-en>Intensive Practice (집중수도) is a concentrated retreat journey held under the direct and personal guidance of Master Mugyeon, Kim Sang-guk. Conducted as 1-night 2-day immersive retreats and regular sessions, practitioners gather to deepen their path through dharma teachings, Life Field cultivation, and the transformative practices of Seongmyeol elevation — stepping beyond the ordinary mind into the light of the whole.</p>
