    <p class="teacher-body r d2" data-en>Master Mugyeon (Kim Sang-guk) continues the lineage of Grandmaster Hanul Kim Jun-won, leading Yeoui Seonwon today. Author of <em>Hanul's Dharma Discourses</em> (한울말씀강론) and the architect of the Yeoui Practice System, he guides practitioners personally through weekly sessions, intensive retreats, and dharma lectures — walking each student along the path of UniO Awakening.</p>
